citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:30pm on January
25, 2024. Inspector knocked on door to the residence and a family member answered the door and informed the inspector
that the licensee was not available.
End Section
